{"word":"G472 - ἀντέχομαι - antéchomai - an-tekh'-om-ahee - Hold fast","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">ἀντέχομαι</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">antéchomai</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">an-tekh'-om-ahee</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Hold fast</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - பற்று, தாங்கு"},{"paragraph":"to hold before or against, hold back, withstand, endure"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G473 - ἀντί - antí - an-tee'/473\">G473</a> and the middle of <a href=\"#/G2192 - ἔχω - échō - ekh'-o/2192\">G2192</a>; to <i>hold</i> oneself <i>opposite</i> to, that is, (by implication) <i>adhere to</i>; by extension to <i>care</i> for: - hold fast, hold to, support.</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>தொடர்புடைய எண்கள் / Cognate: </strong><a href=\"#/G1777/1777\">G1777</a>, <a href=\"#/G2192/2192\">G2192</a>, <a href=\"#/G2722/2722\">G2722</a>, <a href=\"#/G3348/3348\">G3348</a>, <a href=\"#/G3353/3353\">G3353</a>, <a href=\"#/G472/472\">G472</a>, <a href=\"#/G568/568\">G568</a>"}]}